about_text: From Canada 🇨🇦 Ontario...living in the little hamlet of Quadeville Ontario ..also the hide out town for Al Capone in the 1930's...Winters are harsh here at times so my indoor hobbies consist of rock painting and basic sewing projects...love to stencil/paint on canvas and aged pieces of wood...middle aged female that loves and enjoys the piece and freshness of my outdoor flower and vegetable gardens....love to spend time in the kitchen cooking/baking and seasonal preserves...i adore the 70's hippie/boho fashion and contemplating dreads in the near future 😀 ...animal lover ..mothering a miniature corgi that i adopted 6 months ago...
